In MemoQ export the TM. It will have extension .TMX

You have now to download a little tool called Oliphant!

After installation, open it then ctrl+o

Select the .TMX file exported from MemoQ. It will show a little preview of the TM.

Now click on export.

In the new window set 'first attribute' to: ID (even if is not really necessary do it otherwise it could not work the tool)

Select Wordfast file type (.txt)

Now provide a name for the file. Click save.

It will save a .txt file that can be imported with the classic function Import txt, csv in Excel.
